- JIRA task IDs or related PRs
```

The file must be saved as `[PROJECT-IssueNumber]_pr-description.md` in the /tasks folder. It should be clean and ready for copy-paste without editing.

## Output

- A Markdown file named `[PROJECT-IssueNumber]_pr-description.md`
- Follows the projects PR template
- Developers are expected to copy this content into Bitbucket's PR description field